---
layout: base.njk
title: "Academic Blog"
description: "The 10 most recent research notes, code posts, teaching reflections, and academic blog entries."
---
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Academic Blog</p>
  <h1>Research notes, code experiments, and academic reflections.</h1>
  <p>This front page automatically shows the 10 most recent posts and generates category filters from post front matter.</p>
</section>

<section id="blog" aria-labelledby="latest-posts-heading">
  <h2 id="latest-posts-heading">Latest posts</h2>
  <div class="category-tabs" aria-label="Filter posts by category">
    <button class="category-tab is-active" type="button" data-category-filter="all">All</button>
    {% for category in collections.allCategories %}
      <button class="category-tab" type="button" data-category-filter="{{ category }}">{{ category | title }}</button>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="post-grid">
    {% for post in collections.latestPosts %}
      {% include "post-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
